<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Middle-earth is vast and mysterious, full of dangers but also full of rewards for the brave. This page contains a few mild spoilers in order to help you get started. <p>
<em><strong>If you are not a moderator or game developer, please do not edit this page! Thank you. </strong></em> 
</p>
<hr>
 <ol>
<li>
<a href="#head-686e00163995353f74804e1205c6b64a37d25b4b">The towns and dungeons</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-bcb2dbced84e5104371bcbadc7db9085e0e06fb5">Other strange and frightening places</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-4aad2c0f42e4932f5565b4895d4ef9fce2aa8949">Equipment issues</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-899bd694d29ace1be956ab35177075021977560b">Macros</a></li>
<ol>
<li>
<a href="#head-10b07e42427f4f18854b747f7fec756e7ca16057">Keystroke macro (The Hard Way)</a></li>
<li>
<a href="#head-043a7aa40c9413f75c9d9c1f834a81f77dd716de">Macro recorder (The Easy Way)</a></li>
</ol>

<li>
<a href="#head-896d4fbd48be52cb56e32bbd064f743efdbab087">Floor inscriptions</a></li>
